# Ironleaf Landscaping Website

GitHub Pages setup:

1. Upload `index.html` to the root of the repository.
2. Upload the full `images` folder to the root of the repository.
3. Your repo should look like:

```
index.html
images/
  ironleaf-logo.png
  katy-map.png
README.md
```

Do not upload `index_files` and do not use `file:///C:/...` paths.
